        <para>

          This function returns an array of database table information.

        </para>
      </refsect1>
      <refsect1>
        <title>Notes</title>
        <para>

          At current this information is only sparsely documented; more
          documentation on this array and direct database access for developers
          is expected soon.

        </para>
      </refsect1>
      <refsect1>
