      <refsect1>
        <title>Return Values</title>
        <para>

          This function currently returns the name of the
					current top-level module, <parameter>false</parameter> if not 
					in a module.

        </para>
      </refsect1>
      <refsect1>
        <title>Notes</title>
        <para>

 
        </para>
      </refsect1>
