          with the new Dynamic User Data architecture.
          See the User Variable section in the Xaraya Module Development Guide for getting
          an overview of the new architecture.
        </para>
      </refsect1>
      <refsect1>
        <title>Parameters</title>
        <variablelist>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>uid</term>
            <listitem>
