                The user identifier

              </para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
        </variablelist>
      </refsect1>
      <refsect1>
        <title>Return Values</title>
        <para>

          This function returns an associative array of user variables
	  where keys represent variable names and values variable values.

        </para>
      </refsect1>
      <refsect1>
        <title>Notes</title>
